Format 200 150 1
PixelSamples 1 1
ShadingRate 1.0
Option "searchpath" "shader" ["../../shaders:&"]

Display "reverseorientation.tif" "file" "rgba" "string compression" "lzw"

Projection "perspective" "fov" [45.0]
Translate 0 0 5
Rotate 20 1 0 0

WorldBegin
Sides 2

Surface "show_side"
Translate -1.1 0 0
Sphere 1.0 -1.0 1.0 180

Translate 2.2 0 0
ReverseOrientation
Sphere 1.0 -1.0 1.0 180

WorldEnd
